item.title: What are the ClickingMost and client.java in a 508 server?
item.dc:creator: @Lin Lin
item.description:
@Lin wrote:

There’s no clickingMost.java, or TextHandler.java in 508s. Those are classes created by Delta for DeltaScape, and are 317 only. Take a look at the IO -> Packets folder, and then the clicking on a button should be there. For sending text, you still have to call the sendFrame/sendQuest methods.
